      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "Concept ACK.\r\n\r\nBare multisig has not been used for doing multisig transactions in ages. Today their only known use is embedding arbitrary data in transactions that nodes cannot prune from the UTXO set, bloating it forever[^1].\r\n\r\nBare multisig should be treated as an attack vector on Bitcoin nodes, like other constructs that were deemed unsafe and disabled soon after the inception of Bitcoin.\r\n\r\n\r\n[^1]: https://stampchain.io/",
      "created_at" : "2023-08-04T20:29:24Z",
